data.description: 80's Popcorn Ceilings? Gone! Fresh Paint throughout? Yes, along with  new Livingroom and Primary bedroom carpeting. Deep Cleaning completed as well...all fresh and new as of November. This beautiful and spacious 2 bedroom/2 bath upper-level condo in Smyrna IS the Definition of 'Move-In Ready'! Hillsdale condominiums are nestled in a wooded area between The Battery/Truist Park and Smyrna Market Village, with restaurants and  shopping galore. The park-like setting has exquisite landscaping  surrounded by mature woods with new sitting areas throughout the complex; it's a quiet, soothing oasis from the hustle & bustle of Metro  Atlanta. The spacious Primary bedroom has its own updated bathroom along  with walk-through double custom closets. The large second bedroom  is bright and sunny with an updated bathroom. As you go down the hall there is a laundry closet with washer & dryer as well as an updated  HVAC system and water heater. Further down you enter the kitchen with updated cabinets, countertops, sink/faucet, and appliances....and  there is new luxury vinyl flooring throughout the kitchen and hallway.  The kitchen opens to a formal dining room with new French doors that  open to the balcony...perfect for morning breakfast or evening wine. The updates are numerous: Deluxe storm door with lock and sliding  window/screen panel, updated double-bolted front door, crown molding throughout, updated lighting fixtures, including West Elm chandeliers  in Dining Room and Kitchen, ceiling fans throughout, updated  bathroom vanities, mirrors, sinks, toilets, medicine cabinets and tiled  floors, Nest thermostat and smoke detector plus wall mounted TVs in  the Family room and Primary bedroom remain for your viewing  pleasure. This exceptional community includes a beautiful pool, newly renovated  clubhouse, and 2 tennis courts. And it's in Smyrna, with all it has to  offer along with easy access to 285/75; it's an easy commute to The  Atl. and the airport. FHA Approved & No Rental Restrictions!
